### How to read harness files

Each contract file has: **Type** (enforcement mechanism), **Trigger** (when it fires),
**Precondition** (what must be true), **Enforcement** (code or harness),
**Recovery** (what to do on violation), **Escalation** (when to surface to user).

Each skill file has: **Role sequence** (triage/execute/verify), **Stages** with
numbered steps, **Contracts referenced**, and task-specific rules.

